                     <interp inst="t18510707-1532-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 pawnbroker's duplicate, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18510707-name-546" type="victimName">
